    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">ObjectVertexDistance</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">(VertexIndex) returns the distance along the length of the object from the beginning of the object to the vertex indicated by VertexIndex. &#160;Formulas for the third dimension of an object are not taken into consideration when computing ObjectVertexDistance.</text></para>
